title: BONUS: Keke Palmer Talks "Nope" And Much More
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Keke Palmer sits down with Ebro in the Morning to have a great conversation on working with Jordan Peele and actor Daniel Kaluuya, have some UFO and conspiracy talk, the importance in giving opportunities to other women and creatives, and more! 'Nope' is in theaters now.
